title.narrative: Project for Integrated Urban and Tourism Development (PIUTD)

description.narrative: The PDO of the proposed project is to improve urban infrastructure, enhance tourism assets, and strengthen institutional capacity to support tourism-related local economic development in selected areas in the south of Albania.
